            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ἀγαθῇ Τύχῃ <lb n="2"/>Κυρίῳ θεῷ μεγάλῳ Σεράπιδι κα<supplied reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> <lb n="3"/>μ<supplied reason="lost">υριωνύμῳ</supplied> Εἴσιδι καὶ Ἀνούβιδι καὶ <supplied reason="lost">τοῖς</supplied> <lb n="4"/>συννάοις ἐπηκόοις <supplied reason="lost">θεοῖς</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>ανθήιος εὐχ̣αρ<supplied reason="lost">ιστήριον</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>νέθηκ<supplied reason="lost">εν</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Am Anfang Z. 6 stehen zwei Buchstaben / Zeichen, die schwerlich mit der Lesung μ[υριωνύμῳ] zu vereinbaren sind.</p>
            </div>
